<LanguageData>
  <Greenway_MutantCitizenship_ColonistPresent.stages.0.description>變種人作為同胞生活在我們身邊。殖民地因此變得更強大。</Greenway_MutantCitizenship_ColonistPresent.stages.0.description>
  <Greenway_MutantCitizenship_ColonistPresent.stages.0.label>我們當中的突變體</Greenway_MutantCitizenship_ColonistPresent.stages.0.label>
  <Greenway_MutantMasters_MutantColonistPresent.stages.0.description>群體受到突變力量的引導，這是理所當然的。</Greenway_MutantMasters_MutantColonistPresent.stages.0.description>
  <Greenway_MutantMasters_MutantColonistPresent.stages.0.label>突變領導股票</Greenway_MutantMasters_MutantColonistPresent.stages.0.label>
  <Greenway_MutantMasters_NonMutantSlavePresent.stages.0.description>未突變的勞動力在突變的權威之下服務。</Greenway_MutantMasters_NonMutantSlavePresent.stages.0.description>
  <Greenway_MutantMasters_NonMutantSlavePresent.stages.0.label>較少的束縛</Greenway_MutantMasters_NonMutantSlavePresent.stages.0.label>
  <Greenway_MutantPurge_MutantColonistPresent.stages.0.description>變種人在群體內自由生活。這是站不住腳的。</Greenway_MutantPurge_MutantColonistPresent.stages.0.description>
  <Greenway_MutantPurge_MutantColonistPresent.stages.0.label>突變體污染</Greenway_MutantPurge_MutantColonistPresent.stages.0.label>
  <Greenway_MutantPurge_MutantSlavePresent.stages.0.description>即使是被鎖住的突變體仍然是對群體純潔性的冒犯。</Greenway_MutantPurge_MutantSlavePresent.stages.0.description>
  <Greenway_MutantPurge_MutantSlavePresent.stages.0.label>突變體仍可耐受</Greenway_MutantPurge_MutantSlavePresent.stages.0.label>
  <Greenway_MutantSlaves_MutantColonistPresent.stages.0.description>變種人在本應是奴隸的時候卻成為了自由的殖民者。</Greenway_MutantSlaves_MutantColonistPresent.stages.0.description>
  <Greenway_MutantSlaves_MutantColonistPresent.stages.0.label>變種人從鎖鏈中解放出來</Greenway_MutantSlaves_MutantColonistPresent.stages.0.label>
  <Greenway_MutantSlaves_SlaveStatus.stages.0.description>殖民地有變異奴隸可供剝削和控制。</Greenway_MutantSlaves_SlaveStatus.stages.0.description>
  <Greenway_MutantSlaves_SlaveStatus.stages.0.label>鎖鏈中的變異奴隸</Greenway_MutantSlaves_SlaveStatus.stages.0.label>
  <Greenway_MutantSlaves_SlaveStatus.stages.1.description>這裡應該有被鎖鏈鎖住的變異勞動，而不是浪費的自由。</Greenway_MutantSlaves_SlaveStatus.stages.1.description>
  <Greenway_MutantSlaves_SlaveStatus.stages.1.label>沒有變異奴隸</Greenway_MutantSlaves_SlaveStatus.stages.1.label>
  <Greenway_SecondClassMutants_MutantSlavePresent.stages.0.description>在殖民地真正的公民之下，突變種正在被正確使用。</Greenway_SecondClassMutants_MutantSlavePresent.stages.0.description>
  <Greenway_SecondClassMutants_MutantSlavePresent.stages.0.label>突變體保留在原來的位置</Greenway_SecondClassMutants_MutantSlavePresent.stages.0.label>
  <Greenway_Utobitha_MutantColonistPresent.stages.0.description>變種人在這裡，建立屬於他們的未來。</Greenway_Utobitha_MutantColonistPresent.stages.0.description>
  <Greenway_Utobitha_MutantColonistPresent.stages.0.label>尤托比薩生活</Greenway_Utobitha_MutantColonistPresent.stages.0.label>
  <Greenway_Utobitha_NonMutantPresent.stages.0.description>非變種人仍然存在於一個本應屬於變種人的家園。</Greenway_Utobitha_NonMutantPresent.stages.0.description>
  <Greenway_Utobitha_NonMutantPresent.stages.0.label>烏托比薩的外來者</Greenway_Utobitha_NonMutantPresent.stages.0.label>
